<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="dangerous-adj">dangerous <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'deɪndʒərəs/    美 /'deɪndʒərəs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(引起) 危险的； 充满危险的；不安全的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>It is dangerous</strong> to walk on thin ice in a lake. 
在湖面的薄冰上行走是很危险的。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A little knowledge is a dangerous thing. 
浅学误人。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>dangerously /'deɪndʒərəsli/ adv   </p></div>